Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:32.73,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:33.99,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:34.79,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.75,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The man who once owned everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:39.92,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Pirate King,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.10,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.23,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The words he said before his death,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.13,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Sent all the people of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:47.70,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Out to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:50.53,Default,Gold Roger,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:52.34,Default,Gold Roger,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you want it, I'll give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:53.96,Default,Gold Roger,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.61,Default,Gold Roger,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I left everything in that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:59.71,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Men, searching for romance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.59,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Pushed forward towards the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.34,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The world is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:06.35,gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,In the Grand Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is a calm night, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been on watch tonight, but it has been completely calm. {I think sounds better. Previously: I am on ship duty tonight, but it has been completely calm.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steering is completely meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I call, "Breaking a bone for no reason".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am just bone~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have become comrades with Luffy and this crew. {I assume we aren't using Nakama}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are {all}good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that is not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found something amazing during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:03:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In it was{were} the recounting{descriptions} of the crew's amazing adventures and battles{fights}. {I believe this wording works better}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as long as I have become their comrade, I must act appropriately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a waking piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,~White Handkerchief~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun still hasn't risen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us sleep for a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about Brook, and stop Luffy's snoring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:45.10,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)\fscx123.75\fscy123.75\pos(609,170)}Brook's Hard Struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:45.10,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)\fscx90\fscy183.75\pos(622,635)}The Difficult Path to Becoming a True Crewmate? {Title seems a bit off center}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do, Miss. Navigator?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we use the paddles, we can escape{get out of the} this calm{still} water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the weather, I would say it should{will} only stay calm for {about}today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, there is no need to waste my precious cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji's food is the best, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, how about seconds on your seafood salad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been freaking out since this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{What, }Did you see something interesting, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, when he was on watch{ship patrol}, he saw the Voyage Journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes{Yeah}! I just happened to come across it{that}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truthfully, I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My excitement from the Thriller Bark incident had yet to subside{cool down},
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for you{all}, that was{is} just the tip of the iceberg. {SLIGHT SCENE BLEED THOUGH THIS COULD BE LEFT BECAUSE OF HIS CONTINUED SPEECH}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped the rebellion in the sand country of Arabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great adventure in Sky Island, though it's existence was considered a mere legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Followed by the amazing feat of making the World Government an enemy at Water 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so surprising that I thought my heart would pop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! But, I don't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, from here{now} on out, what will we be writing in it? {Honestly I would prefer to use "But from now on..." but this works better with the translation I think}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook will be added to the Voyage Journal too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I have become your comrade, I don't feel like I have been of any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand you getting all worked up, but let me give you a piece of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall listen carefully, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this crew, you must never let your guard down during a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! If it is about that, this "quick draw" Brook shall be ready regardless of when an enemy attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it is already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That food is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think I let my{me} guard down for even a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall work myself to the bone, so that I can be your true comrade as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I was only bone to start out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you are really helping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you are willing to help wash dishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can {relaxedly }prepare tea to take to Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Though}I am really looking forward to helping everyone when something major occurs,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but first I'd like to start out helping everyone with even the smaller things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a great of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A skeleton who wishes to help out with small things, one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I shall take the tea to Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, where shall I put these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drop them even it kills you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that, I am already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say "Bon!"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say "Magnificent"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have had you wash the dishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Then I shall give Nami the tea in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is for me to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have brought the tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind showing me your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THAT ALL OF A SUDDEN?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A map?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we have been pretty busy of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the ship isn't moving, this is a great chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, your dream is to draw a map of the world{ map}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my navigational skills, I will travel {all }the Oceans of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and draw a map of the World that I saw with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is anything I can help with, feel free to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a refill?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, just the thought is more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are an amazing and considerate person, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, you are going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I almost burnt my finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I don't have any skin to burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! The map!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe what I have done. Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, it is so nice and clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THAT IS WRONG, DAMN IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it feels like I haven't helped at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like those two are going to do something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, come and check it out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather is nice, so I am sun-drying my medicinal plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky is going to test his new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing uses cola as energy, and is a high force Super Franky Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to a regular cannon, its accuracy and strength are many times more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That added to my Sniper skills creates{makes} a monstrous combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so excited. My heart is beating so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, if there is anything I can do to help, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think. Well, just to be on the safe side, get another barrel of cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is an easy request. I will do so happily!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cola barrel is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, pour it in right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The target is that rocky outcrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I have locked on to the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {is}strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, increase the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, something seems wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well{Hey}, that{this} was a huge failure. {somehow this sentance seems a little off}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That shouldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This is kinda salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something mixed in with the cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is soy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act all confused! You mixed up the cola and soy barrels, didn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You're right. So that is what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a huge mistake on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking! What were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for you to be talking like some old geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My entire body is soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the plants that I was drying need to be wiped down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This meat has gotten a lot better with the extra soy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How freaking positive can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I have done has backfired on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for me to be admiring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I too am a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meditation I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You control your mental state, and reach a blank slate in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:13:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I shouldn't disturb you by talking, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly feel the need to go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to get my permission for every freakin' thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My legs fell asleep, and I can't stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even have any muscles for your legs to fall asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, pretty soon I am gonna leak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait one second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I do has brought inconvenience to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, is there anything I can help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so unsettled?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsettled?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you are afraid of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is just as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I am unsettled, scared, and I can't bear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Luffy first invited me to join the crew, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those words alone made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, when we all defeated Oz together, I felt so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:25.91,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it ok for me to become your comrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:26.80,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's {is}fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.10,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,EH?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, was it really ok for me to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we are heading into the New World, it is a fact that ridiculously strong enemies will cross our path.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if I were not of any help{ to you all}, and was only a holding you back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{So, }If something like that were to happen, I would need to leave the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:15:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have to return to that lifestyle of living alone for years on end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I too used to be very insecure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit us at http://www.yibis.com
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chat us up at #yibis@irc.rizon.net
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I too used to be very insecure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always afraid that I wasn't suitable to be one of their comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I wanted to give my life for their sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that this would make me suitable to have a been with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:51.38,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,I have gigantic enemies, whom I can't escape from, regardless of where I am on the Seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:55.82,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,My enemy is the world, and that darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:59.55,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I didn't want you to come and save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:04.26,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,If my life will always come with the risk of death, then I want to die here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, you thought that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that was my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True comrades aren't that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure that you'll be fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji {has }put his cooking skills on the line, and {has }made a huge meal{full course} from the sea ingredients he harvested.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will definitely be tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Hurry, and come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it ok that I have joined the Straw Hat Crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was too easy! But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided it, so you will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that, it's time for food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Straw Hat Crew can have such a calm day like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, {we are going}lets go {to }catch dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years... No, how many decades has it been,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since I have been able to take an afternoon nap so comfortably?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.75,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.18,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to be sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.46,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, we can see the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.78,Flashbacks,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a Summer Island! It has a beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:19:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While{When} I wandered{was wandering} the seas alone, I would dream of the time I spent with my comrades or Laboon.{ I would remember see reminiscing moments with comrades or Laboon in my dreams. sorry for the complete rewrite}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be so happy, and when I awoke{jumped awake}, only the pain of my lonely reality was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, sleep was never a peaceful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, if I listen carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this clothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that either of these would{will} suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are comrades so close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I died, and am only bones now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am really glad that I am alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This short time we have now is without a doubt just a break{ time} that will lead into our next adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Time to rest one's bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon. It seems that next time we are to meet, I will have many stories to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you are still waiting and are looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time we get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:23:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I too will work myself to the bone, and put my body on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.82,0:23:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a skeleton though, so I don't have a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally here at{in }the Red Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Island of Mermen is pretty close.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.78,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where the mermaids are?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no mermaids, but a sea monster has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.94,0:23:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we beat him, something came out of his stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.14,0:23:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is... Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.16,0:23:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrival! The Red Line
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will become Pirate King!
